      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA solver must be verified under a documented SQA plan covering version control, regression testing, and release qualification.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2023 R1 is used under a validated SQA plan maintained by DePuy Synthes. Version-controlled solver inputs and automated regression test suites are documented. Achieved level exceeds the required level for Medium model risk."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
